history.content:
Occasionally we have students in the EECS department who are looking for private tutoring. We'd like to have a pool of qualified tutors to draw from when students are looking to hire someone. If you're interested in remaining on our tutor list, please fill out this form and we'll contact you if a need for tutoring arises. Thanks for your willingness to support your fellow students! The departmental tutoring rate is $13.57/hour.
